nodes.text: The Dark Lands was the informal name for one of the districts of Nar Shaddaa, located in the moon's Undercity. The Dark Lands were located directly beneath the Red Light Sector, and were notable for having no electricity. Most of the paths to the district were blocked off, as the Hutts did not want the Dark Lands' criminals to interfere with the business taking place in the Red Light Sector.
